  "_comment": "AI News feed catalog for the mChatAI 'AI News' applet (iOS + macOS). This is the SOURCE OF TRUTH for the news source list. The app fetches this at runtime via NewsFeedCatalogService (raw.githubusercontent, no auth, ~1-day TTL cache, bundled offline fallback), so ADDING/REMOVING a feed is a zero-rebuild git PR. Humans curate additions here; the weekly news-feeds-sync Cloud Function health-checks every URL and stamps healthStatus/lastChecked/lastHttpStatus (the app skips sources marked healthStatus:'dead'). Do NOT hardcode feeds into Swift (CLAUDE.md RULE #1).",
